  <description><![CDATA[<p>Friendly, attentive staff will greet you at this attractive family hotel that is part of the impressive Bella Italia resort of villas, holiday bungalows, apartments and camping. Situated 300m from the lakeside, then from there a 20 minute walk along the promenade to the centre of Peschiera. Located to the far side of the resort and enjoying privacy, the hotel operates independently, ensuring 4 star facilities, pool and sunbathing terraces for hotel guests only.</p>]]></description>
